    <title type="html"><![CDATA[HowTo : Change Jboss 4.2.2GA Web Server Port]]></title>
    <link href="http://noppanit.github.io/howto-change-jboss-422ga-web-server-port/"/>
    <updated>2008-03-27T00:00:00-04:00</updated>
    <id>http://noppanit.github.io/howto-change-jboss-422ga-web-server-port</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p align="left">
  Locate server.xml file in $JBOSS_HOME\\server\\all\\deploy\\jboss-web.deployer\\server.xml
</p>


<p>Change this line to a port that you want it to be.</p>

<p>&lt;Connector port=&#8221;<strong>8081</strong>&#8221; address=&#8221;${jboss.bind.address}&#8221; &#8230;</p>
]]></content>
